  <ThingDef ParentName="BaseInsect">
    <defName>VFEI_VatGrownSpelopede</defName>
    <label>Vat-grown spelopede</label>
    <description>A medium-sized bioengineered bug the size of a sheep. The spelopede is the middle caste of a hive, taking care of most work tasks as well as fighting with its digging claws. A vat-grown creature, it is unable to reproduce, and its lifespan is significantly decreased.</description>
